FuncDef: The display inof configuration status command displays the configuration status on the iNOF network. The display inof configuration status command displays the configuration status on the iNOF network. This command is supported only on the CE6860-SAN, CE6866K, CE6866, CE6860-HAM, CE6885-SAN, CE8850-SAN, CE8851K, CE8851-32CQ8DQ-P and CE8850-HAM.
